name: May Graham
themes: Academic Difficulty, Faculty Support, Peer Relationships, Belonging, Cultural Representation, Financial Struggles, Mental Health, Work-Life Balance, Identity & Discrimination, Personal Growth
description: May Graham, a transfer student and non-binary individual, discusses their struggles with academic difficulty, lack of support, and discrimination in their previous university, contrasted with a positive and supportive environment at Oregon State University. This change has led to personal growth, improved mental health, and a sense of belonging.
